cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with object tracking in video. The use of deep neural networks (cs.LG) and Bayesian optimization (cs.AI) also suggest these sub-categories as likely candidates. Additionally, the use of spatio-temporal information (cs.MM) and the modeling of a dynamic objective function (cs.NE) further support these sub-categories as possible matches.
